#Cau truc
1. Front-End
@LoginWindow
	*Ref:
		#AdminWindow
		#StaffWindow
		#CustomerWindow
	*Function
		Login	<- btn_Login_Click()
		Exit	<- btn_Close_Click()
@AdminWindow: Admin Dashboad
	*Ref:
		<tab>: StaffList
		<tab>: ProductList
		<tab>: Profile
	*Function:
		- StaffList
		Add		<-	btn_Create_Click()
		Edit	<-	btn_Update_Click()
		Remove	<-	btn_Delete_Click()
		- ProductList
		Add		<-	btn_Create_Click()
		Edit	<-	btn_Update_Click()
		Remove	<-	btn_Delete_Click()
@StaffWindow: Employer Dashboad
	*Ref:
		<tab>: ManageUser
		<tab>: ManageOrder
		<tab>: ProductList
		<tab>: Profile
	*Function:
		- ManageUser
		Edit
		- ManageOrder
		Edit	<-	btn_ChangeStatus_Click()
@CustomerWindow: User Dashboad
	*Ref:
		<tab>: ProductList
		<tab>: Order
		<tab>: Cart
		<tab>: Profile
	*Function:
		- ProductList
		- Order
		- Cart
		- Profile
